How to run the service app (will be available at localhost port 5000):

from the command line:
make run


File descriptions:

README - short descriptions of each file and instructions for running the service
Makefile - simple Makefile to interact with provided example code
app.py - example code for a Flask application
auth.py - mock auth service with hard coded user and token information.
db.py - example code for a SQLite database
requirements.txt - list of python requirements to be installed via pip
test_client.py - example code for a requests based test client. We encourage you to add tests, but they are not required
